{"tid":2276891,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"CC台手足：「其實燒山媽咪麵呢種盲目吹奏燈神風氣係咪一種網絡病態？」","createTime":"2020-11-08T05:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T06:09:33.000Z","uid":310914,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"259d80637344b5a0b0127cbba2e43f8f00663d05","tid":2276891,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:58:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實燒山媽咪麵呢種盲目吹奏燈神風氣係咪一種網絡病態？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2276802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2276802</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">呢種風氣起初世界盃笑下比利\n自從有網絡kol出現，呢種風氣慢慢愈黎愈病態\n先唔講呢兩位已經破過好多次燈\n每次有咩大事件討論，總有一班信徒開post吹奏\n仲有一班人成日綑綁連登仔性格\n明明係一班龍蛇混雜既連登仔，但專登塑造成一個神憎鬼厭既人\n其實用以上呢兩種手段，連登好難再有有營養既post\n\n\n</code></pre>"},{"pid":"37c1f3b17379319ed559470aec72d04aea59a4fd","tid":2276891,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:59:13.000Z","msg":"Post錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96747c74c0056584e632cb779ff124e39d1e148e","tid":2276891,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"Post錯台，唔該Admin幫手搬過財經台<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf2c15a002f34a6cae234c67519162c816f6321","tid":2276891,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:09:33.000Z","msg":"其實係"}],"pinned":{"pid":"96747c74c0056584e632cb779ff124e39d1e148e","tid":2276891,"uid":310914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T06:00:50.000Z","msg":"Post錯台，唔該Admin幫手搬過財經台<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}